{"tid":2185635,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"仲兩頭望？香港大學（XGU）開始清算學生喇","createTime":"2020-09-02T11:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T05:51:39.000Z","uid":80567,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9268811fa316e5d179e3c766bff56aaccc2b59f3","tid":2185635,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"港大校方譴責校園電視惡搞迎新片 要求移除片段並道歉<br />\n【學苑專訊】香港大學校方今日（9月2日）於Facebook專頁發文[1]，指香港大學中央管理小組[2]（Senior Management Team）已就香港大學學生會校園電視（Campus TV, HKUSU；下稱校園電視）早前發布的改版校園迎新影片[3] 一事向校園電視主席游展鵬發信，並公開信件的完整內容。<span class=\"red\">校方於信中指該影片包含欺凌及仇恨言論，校方就此譴責並要求校園電視移除相關片段及道歉。</span><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/posts/4576037339076620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fundergradnews%2Fposts%2F4576037339076620&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXFLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=56e88b38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/posts/4576037339076620</a><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">XGU聲明全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkuofficial/posts/2697170217227113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkuofficial%2Fposts%2F2697170217227113&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXFLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=67b2b56b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkuofficial/posts/2697170217227113</a></span><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得尋晚有個post係講城大校媒因為「同學各位找郭.位」而被秋後算帳<br />\n<blockquote>［城大］學生因 「城大各位找郭位」片被學校秋後算帳並要寫道歉信俾郭位<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n校園係捍衛言論自由嘅堡壘<br />\n校媒應有出版自由<br />\n學生應有免於恐懼嘅自由<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如果港大從來都為言論自由設限<br />\n當初就唔會出到香港民族論呢一本書</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\nInstagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/CEl3wGBJnFf/?igshid=1tnl0s690sht6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCEl3wGBJnFf%2F%3Figshid%3D1tnl0s690sht6&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXFLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=a24db1b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/CEl3wGBJnFf/?igshid=1tnl0s690sht6</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/3257468364321837/?vh=e&amp;extid=DutMHMYk4q05DWt7&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F3257468364321837%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DDutMHMYk4q05DWt7%26d%3Dn&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXFLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=047baa03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/3257468364321837/?vh=e&amp;extid=DutMHMYk4q05DWt7&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">CLS 推爆條片<br />\n去校方個page洗版<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>起初，納粹抓共產黨人的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是共產黨人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓猶太人的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是猶太人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓工會成員的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是工會成員。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓天主教人的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是天主教人。<br />\n<br />\n最後當他們來抓我時，<br />\n再也沒有人站起來為我說話了。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8af1c462dedd1b164aead2041ff36a9297560cc1","tid":2185635,"uid":221013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7cd9f2c437328e63d7dda89a0d381b8173a30290","tid":2185635,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"XGU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c076b6956adf3a8edcbb1d9268774b762dfb2f0","tid":2185635,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:33:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bf5705ffa85878ebecd190588d6f88eef8d9691","tid":2185635,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fea7fb81b25b51ee65eeaf187b848881c3ffde9","tid":2185635,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"